<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fire-v">fire <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'faɪə(r)/    美 /'faɪər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>放 (枪、炮等)；射击：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>fire a shot</strong>
开枪</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>fire a gun</strong> at the enemy
向敌人开枪</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you come any nearer, I will fire.
你再靠近，我就开枪了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-dismiss">2.★ <strong>解雇 (dismiss)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The airline <strong>fired</strong> him <strong>for</strong> being drunk.
他因为醉酒被航空公司开除了。</p></div></div>